author: Lucas Nolan, Lucas Nolan
title: Jeff Bezos: Amazon Will Work with WHO to Fight Coronavirus Epidemic
description: Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos recently stated via social media that he had spoken with the Director General of the WHO to discuss the coronavirus outbreak and hinted that Amazon may deliver test kits globally.
content:
